# Launch focus — functional OS (LAUNCH-functional-os)

**Default Agent mode:** ship **end-to-end functionality** for Player OS, Parent OS, and Coach OS workspaces. Polish and custom visual systems are secondary until owner reopens dedicated tracks.

## MUST NOT (without owner reopen)

- Implement visuals from Gemini Deep Research exports in [`docs/vision/references/ui/research/`](../../docs/vision/references/ui/research/)
- Ship custom platform chrome PNGs or Flow-generated UI artwork from research briefs
- Wire avatar PNG layers, Photopea pipelines, or character sheets — see [`avatar-builder-deferred.mdc`](./avatar-builder-deferred.mdc)
- Run **3.5m-gemini-ingest**, **3.5m-gate**, or **3.6b+** Avatar Studio work

## MAY (launch-critical)

- Fix broken loops, dead CTAs, and route/import blockers on `/player/*`, `/parent/*`, `/coach/*`
